<title>
"Characterizing core journals in ophthalmology literature using Bradfor" by Leo Meller, Vasan Jagadeesh et al.
</title>
 

<!-- FILE article_meta-tags.inc --><!-- FILE: /srv/sequoia/main/data/assets/site/article_meta-tags.inc -->
<meta itemprop="name" content="Characterizing core journals in ophthalmology literature using Bradford’s law: a bibliometric analysis">
